Package: rrenko
Type: Package
Title: An R Package for Renko Charts
Version: 0.1.4
Author: Roman Abashin
Maintainer: Roman Abashin <mail@romanabashin.com>
Description: An R package to efficiently build Renko charts with ggplot2 and data.table. Renko charts are used to filter the noise in volatile stock movements. 
Acknowledgement: Inspired by the question of Stackoverflow user mea43 (6411051). Time series algorithm by Sotos (5635580). 
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
